Desc: An organ that demonstrates Trinity's beautiful artistic tastes. You can feel a certain holiness just by looking at it.

Name: Tea Party Table
Desc: A tea party table with a delicate design. Despite its beautiful appearance, it's also a place where serious discussions are sometimes held.

Name: Interrogation Room Table
Desc: A mysterious table that makes you tell the truth. The moment you sit down, you'll reveal the secrets you've been hiding.

Name: Prayer Chair
Desc: A prayer chair to sit in humbly. It will ease your heart and mind.

Name: D.U. Shiratori City Diorama Table
Desc: A table that tells you the state of restoration of D.U. Shiratori City. Let's take a moment to feel proud.

Name: Weedy Garden
Desc: This seems like your average, well-maintained indoor garden at first glance. However, upon closer glance, this thriving garden only seems to be growing weeds.

Name: Hyakkiyako Merch Display
Desc: This carefully arranged display is made of some of Hyakkiyako's most popular merchandise. Many students would be willing to take out a Kaiser loan for these collectibles.

Name: Game Development Department Locker
Desc: A locker found in the Game Development Department. Its decorations give it a cozy feel.

Name: Deep Blue Silver Stool
Desc: A deep blue stool that is cool to the touch. Its silver base gives it a sophisticated look.

Name: Sky Blue Sofa Chair
Desc: A light blue sofa meant to fit just one person. It's super soft.

Name: Steel Sliding Cabinet
Desc: A large cabinet with lots of storage space and a sliding door to keep it secure. Cats seem to love it as well.

Name: Chinese Hot Food Display
Desc: This display cabinet is stocked with delicious food and plenty of soy sauce bottles. It's guaranteed to keep your food warm.

Name: Luxurious Chinese Chair
Desc: This luxurious Chinese-style chair is made of expensive hardwood and decorated with soft curtains. Its the perfect place to relax.

Name: Woodworking Workbench
Desc: This well-equipped woodworking workbench has everything you need for any project. Time seems to fly once you start working.

Name: Fresh Fish Coolers
Desc: These coolers are full of freshly caught fish. Make sure the lid is on tight so they don't escape!

Name: Scuba Diving Gear Rack
Desc: This clothing rack is equipped with anything you might need for a deep dive at any time!

Name: Portable Shower Stand
Desc: This portable shower can run both cold and hot water to keep you clean wherever you go!

Name: Mechanical Marlin Decor
Desc: This giant marlin decoration looks just like the real thing. Be careful! It might start flopping around!

Name: Problem Solver 68 Band Stage
Desc: Rock out and be bad! This stage thrills with the excitement of Problem Solver 68.

Name: Classic Pattern Travel Bag
Desc: A classic travel bag. Combines elegance and practicality. Perfect for sophisticated travelers.

Name: Mini Stool and Sun Bed
Desc: A small stool and sun bed with a side of refreshing juice. The checkered cushions add coziness.

Name: Ice Cream Table
Desc: A table with a sweet ice cream treat on it. Melt away the summer heat.

Name: Sunshine Lemon Tree
Desc: A lemon tree bursting with fresh lemons. Turn on the tap for a refreshing drink!

Name: Board Game Table
Desc: A board game table with an old map, pieces, and dice spread out on top. It looks like it's game night.

Name: Classic Library Chair
Desc: A cozy, retro library chair. This is the chair of dreams for serious readers.

Name: Manuscript Work Desk
Desc: A must-have for authors finishing up their manuscript! Ignite your passion!

Name: Resting Bench Table
Desc: Made from strong, lightweight materials, this resting bench table is suitable for any location.

Name: Origami Table
Desc: An old-fashioned origami table to help clear one's mind. A noble hobby for a young lady.

Name: Momo Friends Merch Kiosk
Desc: A merch kiosk filled with Momo Friends goods. You can't help but fall in love with the cuteness.

Name: Fresh Shop Table
Desc: A fusion of neatness and nature! A Fresh Shop table. How about a bowl of fresh fruit?

Name: Tarot Table
Desc: A tarot table where destiny is right here, right now. Which card will come up next?

Name: Antique Countertop
Desc: A counter for cooking everything from warm soup to grilled fish!

Name: Relaxation Chair
Desc: A comfy chair made for rest and relaxation. It's perfect for those who prefer the indoors.

Name: Ice Pool
Desc: Relax in the invigorating water of this ice-cold pool.

Name: Camping Partition
Desc: This partition is perfect for camping with its matching folding chair and cute design.

Name: Camping Coffee Table
Desc: Enjoy a fragrant cup of coffee in nature with this portable table!
